caption.title: Two-dimensional gel electrophoresis of me_SWH-treated MSCs before (a) and after induction for neuronal differentiation for 5 days (b).
caption.p: The spot images of nucleoside diphosphate kinase A (NM23-H1) in different gels from me_SWH-treated MSCs before (upper panel) and after induction (lower panel) are also shown.
